<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٤٦]</span> شرح المفصل ٦/ ٩٤-٩٥.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٤٧]</span> شرح المفصل ٦/ ٩٤-٩٥.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
